Swept up in the magical world of Caraval, Donatella Dragna has finally escaped her father and saved her sister Scarlett from a disastrous arranged marriage. But Tella isn''t yet free. She made a desperate bargain with a mysterious criminal, and what Tella owes him no one has ever been able to deliver: Caraval Master Legend''s true name. To win Caraval, Tella throws herself into the legendary competition once more-- and into the path of the murderous heir to the throne, a doomed love story, and a web of secrets... including her sister''s. If Tella can''t deliver Legend''s name, she''ll lose everything-- maybe even her life.', 'Donatella Dragna embarks on a perilous new game in the enchanting yet deadly world of Caraval to uncover Legend''s identity and fulfill a dangerous bargain.', 1910, '143287375X', '9781432873752', 102, NULL, 684, 'https://covers.openlibrary.org/b/id/9242465-L.jpg', '/works/OL19748577W', NULL, 'Feb 01, 2020', 'English', NULL, 1, 0, 'legendary-stephanie-garber', 0, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 'public', '2026-03-16 15:18:30', '2026-03-22 20:32:05');
